{"id":478,"parent_id":454,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":478,"title":"Job 24","subtitle":"","short_title":"Job","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 24"],[".studySummary",["i","Murderers, adulterers, those who oppress the poor, and wicked people in general often go unpunished for a little while."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.1","order":"02.19.024.34034"},["b","1"],"Why, seeing times are not hidden from the Almighty, do they that know him not see his days?"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.2","order":"02.19.024.34035"},["b","2"],["i","Some"],"remove the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"landmarks"],"; they violently take away flocks, and feed",["i","thereof."]],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.3","order":"02.19.024.34036"},["b","3"],"They drive away the ass of the fatherless, they take the widow’s ox for a pledge."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.4","order":"02.19.024.34037"},["b","4"],"They turn the needy out of the way: the poor of the earth hide themselves together."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.5","order":"02.19.024.34038"},["b","5"],"Behold,",["i","as"],"wild asses in the desert, go they forth to their work; rising betimes for a prey: the wilderness",["i","yieldeth"],"food for them",["i","and"],"for",["i","their"],"children."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.6","order":"02.19.024.34039"},["b","6"],"They reap",["i","every one"],"his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"corn"],"in the field: and they gather the vintage of the wicked."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.7","order":"02.19.024.34040"},["b","7"],"They cause the naked to lodge without clothing, that",["i","they have"],"no covering in the cold."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.8","order":"02.19.024.34041"},["b","8"],"They are wet with the showers of the mountains, and embrace the rock for want of a shelter."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.9","order":"02.19.024.34042"},["b","9"],"They pluck the fatherless from the breast, and take a pledge of the poor."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.10","order":"02.19.024.34043"},["b","10"],"They cause",["i","him"],"to go naked without clothing, and they take away the sheaf",["i","from"],"the hungry;"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.11","order":"02.19.024.34044"},["b","11"],["i","Which"],"make oil within their walls,",["i","and"],"tread",["i","their"],"winepresses, and suffer thirst."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.12","order":"02.19.024.34045"},["b","12"],"Men groan from out of the city, and the soul of the wounded crieth out: yet God",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"layeth"],"not folly",["i","to them."]],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.13","order":"02.19.024.34046"},["b","13"],"They are of those that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"rebel"],"against the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"light"],"; they know not the ways thereof, nor abide in the paths thereof."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.14","order":"02.19.024.34047"},["b","14"],"The murderer rising with the light killeth the poor and needy, and in the night is as a thief."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.15","order":"02.19.024.34048"},["b","15"],"The eye also of the adulterer waiteth for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"twilight"],", saying, No eye shall see me: and disguiseth",["i","his"],"face."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.16","order":"02.19.024.34049"},["b","16"],"In the dark they dig through houses,",["i","which"],"they had marked for themselves in the daytime: they know not the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"light"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.17","order":"02.19.024.34050"},["b","17"],"For the morning",["i","is"],"to them even as the shadow of death: if",["i","one"],"know",["i","them, they are in"],"the terrors of the shadow of death."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.18","order":"02.19.024.34051"},["b","18"],"He",["i","is"],"swift as the waters; their portion is cursed in the earth: he beholdeth not the way of the vineyards."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.19","order":"02.19.024.34052"},["b","19"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"Drought"],"and heat consume the snow waters:",["i","so doth"],"the grave",["i","those which"],"have sinned."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.20","order":"02.19.024.34053"},["b","20"],"The womb shall forget him; the worm shall feed sweetly on him; he shall be no more remembered; and wickedness shall be broken as a tree."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.21","order":"02.19.024.34054"},["b","21"],"He evil entreateth the barren",["i","that"],"beareth not: and doeth not good to the widow."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.22","order":"02.19.024.34055"},["b","22"],"He draweth also the mighty with his power: he riseth up, and no",["i","man"],"is sure of life."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.23","order":"02.19.024.34056"},["b","23"],["i","Though"],"it be given him",["i","to be"],"in safety, whereon he resteth; yet his eyes",["i","are"],"upon their ways."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.24","order":"02.19.024.34057"},["b","24"],"They are exalted for a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"little while"],", but are gone and brought",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"low"],"; they are taken out of the way as all",["i","other,"],"and cut off as the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_24c"},"tops"],"of the ears of corn."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.25","order":"02.19.024.34058"},["b","25"],"And if",["i","it be"],"not",["i","so"],"now, who will make me a liar, and make my speech nothing worth?"]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.2a","order":"02.19.024.34059"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/19.14"},"Deut. 19:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/22.28"},"Prov. 22:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/5.10"},"Hosea 5:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.6a","order":"02.19.024.34061"},["b","6a"],["span.small","HEB"],"fodder."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.12a","order":"02.19.024.34063"},["b","12a"],["span.small","OR"],"does not give heed to their prayer."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.13a","order":"02.19.024.34065"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/2.23.19-24"},"1 Ne. 2:23 (19–24)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/15.26"},"Mosiah 15:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.21.20-22"},"D&C 10:21 (20–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.13b","order":"02.19.024.34067"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/13.29"},"Hel. 13:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.15a","order":"02.19.024.34069"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/7.9.9-10"},"Prov. 7:9 (9–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.16a","order":"02.19.024.34071"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.21"},"D&C 10:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.19a","order":"02.19.024.34073"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/drought"},"TG Drought"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.24a","order":"02.19.024.34075"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/37.10.10-11"},"Ps. 37:10 (10–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.24b","order":"02.19.024.34077"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/26.10"},"2 Ne. 26:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"24c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/24.24c","order":"02.19.024.34079"},["b","24c"],["span.small","HEB"],"heads of grain."]]}
